##  Key Analysis Performed

* Data cleaning and preparation
* Data validation using business rules
* KPI analysis using SQL queries
* Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) using Python
* Dashboard creation in Power BI

---

##  Key Insights

* Fraud patterns identified in claims data
* High-risk customer segments detected
* Claim amount distribution analyzed
* Regional and seasonal trends observed

---

##  Learnings

* Importance of data validation before analysis
* Building business KPIs using SQL
* Performing EDA using Python
* Creating interactive dashboards in Power BI

